msgid "Speed Instinct"
msgstr "迅捷本能"

msgid "Only while this mutation is selected, weapon attack speed increases with active Boss Cells: 0 cells +0%, 1 cell +20%, 2 cells +30%, 3-4 cells +40%, 5 cells +50%."
msgstr "只有选择这项变异时，武器攻击速度才会随已激活 Boss 细胞提高：0 细胞 +0%，1 细胞 +20%，2 细胞 +30%，3-4 细胞 +40%，5 细胞 +50%。"

msgid "The harsher the island becomes, the faster your hands remember how to survive."
msgstr "岛屿越险恶，你的双手就越快想起该如何活下去。"
